HEADWORD: Rigel
<hw>Ri"gel</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Ar. <ets>rijl</ets>,
properly, foot.]</ety> <fld>(Astron.)</fld> <def>A fixed star of the
first magnitude in the left foot of the constellation Orion.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>Regel</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

